  <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question"><span>Why is my garage door so loud?</span><span class="faq-arrow">&#9654;</span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Noise often comes from worn rollers, loose hardware, or lack of lubrication. We can pinpoint the source and quiet things down with the right repair or tune-up.</p></div></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question"><span>Can you repair broken garage door panels?</span><span class="faq-arrow">&#9654;</span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>In some cases, yes—especially if the damage is cosmetic or isolated. We’ll let you know whether a repair or panel replacement makes more sense.</p></div></div>
